&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ cloc .
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">106&lt;/span> text files.
